{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "原初之力 第24章 2-2 灵魂的恸哭",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "王子通过与黑暗魔力同化的席菈灵魂\\n得知了昔日勒福克斯变故的真相。\\n原来唤来黑暗魔力毁灭勒福克斯的\\n正是席菈。为了将此事告知伙伴们，\\n王子带着席菈原路返回。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "席菈的灵魂",
            "context": "是我……是我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "与席菈身体分离的心……\\n不，应该说是席菈的灵魂吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（席菈之所以想要一起来，\\n是因为这里有自己的灵魂啊。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（不过她的灵魂似乎非常痛苦。\\n好像是在因悔恨而呻吟着……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（而且这里的黑暗魔力\\n比其它地方更加浓重。\\n是席菈的灵魂招来的黑暗魔力吗？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "席菈，你究竟经历了什么？\\n为什么你会在这种地方独自……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈的灵魂",
            "context": "我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "席菈？不，这是……\\n席菈的记忆吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸，打扰一下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "噢……你来啦。\\n抱歉，刚才正在想些事情。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我能理解您有很多事情要发愁，\\n毕竟眼下是这种状况。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "但您也要好好吃饭休息啊。\\n要是一国之主都病倒了，\\n才真的会让国家陷入困境呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "来，我拜托厨师做了宵夜，\\n您多少吃一点吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯，谢谢。\\n那我就吃一点吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸……\\n有没有什么我能帮得上忙的事啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "虽然我不懂打仗的事情，\\n但我也不想眼睁睁地\\n看着百姓们受苦受难。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我什么都愿意做，所以……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "没有能让你做的事情。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "战争是关乎两个国家存亡的博弈，\\n并不是有着善心就能帮得上忙的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "您说得对……对不起……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "抱歉啊，是我说得太重了。\\n不过，这场战争我会处理好的。\\n你就相信你的父王吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我并不是不相信您。\\n只是很愧疚于自己什么忙都帮不上……\\n所以想要做些什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我也想要帮上爸爸和大家的忙，\\n我也想要守护这个国家。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "你真是个善良的孩子……\\n所以我才不想让你\\n参与到战争当中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "不过……既然如此，\\n能拜托你帮忙处理一下\\n国内的事务吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "如你所见，\\n我现在已经分身乏术了。\\n你能帮帮爸爸吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "嗯！当然了，爸爸！\\n那我该怎么做呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "有报告称某地出现了异象，\\n希望你能代我去那里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "出现异象的是——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "这里就是“龙之墓”啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "调查员",
            "context": "据说这里是远古时代\\n身为世界根基的原初之龙\\n所沉睡的地方。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "调查员",
            "context": "自勒福克斯建国以来，\\n国家就一直管理并保护着这片区域。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "所以才会需要有王族在场\\n监督调查过程啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "所以这里究竟发生了\\n怎样的异象？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "调查员",
            "context": "湖泊在短时间内被迅速污染，\\n生物的异常死亡和狂暴化。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "调查员",
            "context": "这勒福湖是维持着勒福克斯\\n日常所需的重要水源。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "调查员",
            "context": "若是这湖里的水没法再用的话，\\n国民们的生活会受到很大影响。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "原来如此。\\n看来无论如何都要尽快查明原因\\n并解决问题才行……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我们再去前面看看吧。\\n开始调查。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "公主，您没事吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "嗯，我没事。谢谢你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（这里竟然会出现魔兽，\\n怎么想都不正常。\\n究竟是因为什么呢……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "嗯？这是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "唔……呃啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "诶！？你怎么了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120163_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "唔啊啊啊……啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "这！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "公主！请您……快逃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（大家都在触碰这瘴气之后\\n立刻发生了变化……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（莫非这瘴气就是在龙之墓\\n引发异象的根源！？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "来人啊！\\n还有神志清醒的人吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "调查员",
            "context": "唔嘎啊、啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（所有人都发疯了……\\n以我一己之力救不了他们……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "原谅我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "爸爸……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "辛苦你了，席菈。\\n你心里很不好受吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "不好受的并不是我，\\n而是调查团的人们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我只能眼睁睁地看着\\n大家一个个失去理智，\\n然后抛弃大家自己逃跑……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我什么都做不到……\\n我果然是个废物……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "这不怪你。\\n你有责任心是件好事，\\n但也不必过度自责。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "可是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "就算只有你一个人平安回来，\\n我也已经很庆幸了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "今天就好好休息吧。\\n晚安，席菈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（我怎么可以因为自己没事\\n就感到庆幸。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（所有人都发了疯，\\n所有人都自相残杀之下，\\n只有我一个人得救……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "不对……\\n为什么只有我一个人安然无恙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（对了。当时我也触碰到了\\n那可疑的瘴气，可我却没事。\\n是巧合吗？还是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我要再去那里看看。\\n这次就我一个人去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "这里就是瘴气的源头啊……\\n竟然是世界产生了裂缝导致的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "裂缝通向的是异界吗？\\n还是其它的什么地方？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（距离如此之近我也没有受到任何影响。\\n果然是我对这瘴气有抗性吗？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（虽然不知道为何会有抗性，\\n但能阻止这一切的\\n就只有我一人……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "只要让这裂缝闭合，\\n就能阻断瘴气。\\n得赶快想想办法才行。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0079",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（可就这样关闭裂缝\\n真的是最佳的选择吗……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0080",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（这瘴气确实十分可怕。\\n但只要正确使用，\\n它也可以成为一种强大的武器。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0081",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（或许能够\\n为勒福克斯带来希望……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0082",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我这是在想些什么……\\n得赶快回去\\n找出让裂缝闭合的方法才是。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0083",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（若是对那瘴气拥有抗性的我\\n能够操控那瘴气的话，\\n也许就能拯救勒福克斯。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0084",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（勒福克斯的希望……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0085",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我想要守护心爱之人，想要守护祖国。\\n无力的我终于也有了可以帮忙的机会。\\n爱国心和正义感驱使着我前进。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0086",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "若是告诉爸爸的话，一定会遭到反对。\\n所以我独自展开了研究。\\n直到……那一天的到来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0087",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（现在已经能够确定\\n这瘴气实质上就是黑暗魔力。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0088",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（这裂缝连接着异界空间，\\n遍布异界空间的黑暗魔力\\n则通过裂缝流入了这个世界。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0089",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（不知为何，我拥有对黑暗魔力的抗性，\\n现在也多多少少能够控制\\n一些黑暗魔力……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0090",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "我要召唤更多的黑暗魔力\\n流入这个世界，\\n然后由我来操控。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0091",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "再把它们投放到\\n觊觎勒福克斯的敌国……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0092",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "调查员",
            "context": "唔嘎啊、啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0093",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120162_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0094",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（我很清楚自己打算做的事情\\n非常残忍。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0095",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（但为了保护勒福克斯，\\n我别无选择。\\n此事也必须要由我来做。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0096",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "开始吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0097",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（还差一点……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0098",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0099",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0100",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（黑暗魔力失控了！？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0101",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "（没法停下来，\\n我控制不了这么多的黑暗魔力。\\n这样下去会蔓延到国内……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0102",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "停下！这不是……我想要的！\\n求你了……停下来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0103",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "不要啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0104",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈的灵魂",
            "context": "都是……我的错……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0105",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "席菈！\\n你之所以会那么做，\\n都是为了保护祖国不是吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0106",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以你不必这般自责……\\n席菈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0107",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈的灵魂",
            "context": "都是……我的错……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0108",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔，不行吗。\\n似乎没办法沟通……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0109",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（毁灭勒福克斯的黑暗魔力\\n竟然是席菈唤来的。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0110",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（而即便只有灵魂留在这里，\\n也仍不断地从异界空间\\n召唤黑暗魔力吗。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0111",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "都是……我的错？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0112",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "席菈……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0113",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们先回大家那里一趟吧。\\n把在这里看到的事情告诉大家。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0114",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "看来，不想办法解决一下\\n你的心的问题，我们就没法继续前进。\\n只是，至于解决的办法……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0115",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0116",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（不毁灭席菈的灵魂的话，\\n就无法继续前进。可若是如此，\\n席菈就再也无法取回自己的心。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0117",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "（迦道夫会怎么说呢……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_24_03_0118",
